This paper discusses the use of natural language processing and machine learning techniques for information extraction and summarization, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning (cs.AI) and the potential for scalability (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of semantic parsing (cs.IR) and the generation of story highlights (cs.NE).
